ADDITIONAL TERMS AND CONDITIONS

1. AGRICULTURAL DATA USAGE
   - This software is designed specifically for agricultural and farming purposes
   - Any use of the machine learning models and algorithms should comply with 
     local agricultural regulations and guidelines
   - Users are responsible for verifying AI-generated recommendations with 
     qualified agricultural experts

2. THIRD-PARTY INTEGRATIONS
   - This software integrates with various third-party services including but 
     not limited to:
     * Firebase (Google Cloud Platform)
     * Weather API services
     * Maps and location services
     * Payment processing services
   - Users must comply with the terms of service of these third-party providers
   - The license holder is not responsible for changes in third-party service 
     availability or terms

3. MACHINE LEARNING MODELS
   - The AI models included in this software are provided for educational and 
     agricultural assistance purposes
   - Model predictions should not be considered as definitive agricultural advice
   - Users should consult with agricultural experts for critical farming decisions
   - The accuracy of AI predictions may vary based on image quality, environmental 
     conditions, and regional factors

4. DATA PRIVACY AND SECURITY
   - This software collects and processes agricultural data, location information,
     and user-generated content
   - Users are responsible for complying with local data protection regulations
     (GDPR, CCPA, etc.)
   - Any modifications to the software must maintain the same level of data 
     security and privacy protection

5. COMMERCIAL USE
