     * Maintain the open-source nature of any modifications (if redistributed)
     * Not misrepresent the software's capabilities or accuracy

6. DISCLAIMER OF WARRANTIES
   - This software is provided for agricultural assistance and educational purposes
   - The authors make no warranties regarding the accuracy of agricultural 
     recommendations, weather forecasts, or AI predictions
   - Users assume all risks associated with farming decisions based on software 
     recommendations
